TITLE: Write Constraints Access Policy for Observations (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This AccessPolicy implements write constraints on the 'Observation' resource using FHIRPath expressions. It prevents changes to the 'status' field once an observation is marked as 'final' and requires the 'subject' field to be set when the status is finalized. The `%before` variable refers to the resource state before the write.
