TITLE: Defining a ValueSet in FHIR
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates a FHIR `ValueSet` resource. It defines a group of codes from one or more code systems that relate to a common use case. The example includes codes explicitly listed from LOINC and codes included based on their relationships within the SNOMED CT code system, specifically descendants of the concept with code '118227000'.
SOURCE: https://github.com/medplum/medplum/blob/main/packages/docs/docs/terminology/index.md#_snippet_3

