TITLE: Create Media Resource with External URL (Python)
DESCRIPTION: This Python code snippet demonstrates how to create a Media resource with a URL pointing to an external resource. It uses the `requests` library to make a POST request to the Medplum FHIR server. It sets the `Authorization` header for authentication and includes the Media resource in the request body. The `status` is a required field.
