TITLE: Updating RDS Cluster Parameters in CDK Config (JS)
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how to update the RDS cluster parameters in the CDK config file. The `rdsClusterParameters` object contains the desired Postgres parameters, such as `statement_timeout`, `default_transaction_isolation`, and `auto_explain` settings. This configuration triggers database restarts when deployed.
