TITLE: Healthcheck Artillery Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Configures an Artillery load test for the /healthcheck endpoint. It defines the target URL, test phases (warm-up and ramp-up), and a scenario involving repeated GET requests to the /healthcheck endpoint.
SOURCE: https://github.com/medplum/medplum/blob/main/packages/docs/docs/self-hosting/load-testing.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
# healthcheck.yml

config:
  target: 'https://api.staging.medplum.com'
  phases:
    - duration: 10
      arrivalRate: 10
      name: Warm up
    - duration: 300
      arrivalRate: 10
      rampTo: 100
      name: Ramp up load

scenarios:
  - name: 'Healthcheck'
    flow:
      - loop:
          - get:
              url: '/healthcheck'
        count: 10
```

