TITLE: Representing Coded Values using CodeableConcept in FHIR
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to represent a coded value using the `CodeableConcept` data type in FHIR.  It includes an array of `Coding` objects, each representing a code from a different code system (LOINC and SNOMED CT). The `text` field provides a human-readable representation of the concept.
