TITLE: Patient Chart Flow Diagram
DESCRIPTION: This Mermaid diagram visualizes the relationship between a Patient resource and other FHIR resources used in charting, such as Observation, Condition, AllergyIntolerance, MedicationRequest, Immunization, and RiskAssessment. It illustrates how these resources are linked to a patient, providing a visual representation of patient data relationships.
