TITLE: Write-only/Dual Write Sequence Diagram (Mermaid)
DESCRIPTION: This Mermaid sequence diagram illustrates the write-only/dual write phase, where write requests are sent to both the existing database and Medplum.  It highlights the data flow from the Client, through the Existing API, to both the Existing DB and Medplum, ensuring that new data is captured in both systems during the initial migration phase.  The diagram shows confirmation messages returned to the Existing API and then to the Client.
