TITLE: Defining ValueSet in FHIR (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a ValueSet resource to define a grouping of codes from a CodeSystem. The ValueSet resource includes a canonical URL and a `compose` element with an `include` element that references the entire CodeSystem by its URL.
