DESCRIPTION: Defines a FHIR Measure resource with a single group and population using application/x-fhir-query for the criteria. The measure is set to active status and includes a URL for identification. The expression Patient signifies that all patients will be included in the population.
SOURCE: https://github.com/medplum/medplum/blob/main/packages/docs/docs/api/fhir/operations/evaluate-measure.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "resourceType": "Measure",
  "status": "active",
  "url": "https://example.com/test-measure",
  "group": [
    {
      "population": [
        {
          "code": {
            "coding": [
              {
                "code": "measure-population"
              }
            ]
          },
          "criteria": {
            "language": "application/x-fhir-query",
            "expression": "Patient"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

