TITLE: Read from Medplum Sequence Diagram (Mermaid)
DESCRIPTION: This Mermaid sequence diagram illustrates the process of reading data from Medplum using a feature flag.  The diagram highlights how the Client's read request is routed either to the Existing API or the Medplum API based on the state of the Feature Flag. This allows for controlled testing and rollout of Medplum's read capabilities.
