TITLE: Mermaid Diagram of Labs & Imaging Workflow
DESCRIPTION: This Mermaid diagram illustrates the relationships between Patient, ServiceRequest, Specimen, Observation, and DiagnosticReport resources in a typical Labs & Imaging workflow.  It shows how a patient's ServiceRequest leads to a Specimen collection, which then generates Observations, and ultimately a DiagnosticReport.
