TITLE: PostCSS Configuration File
DESCRIPTION: Configures PostCSS with the Mantine preset and custom variables.  The `postcss.config.mjs` file defines the PostCSS plugins, including the Mantine preset and `postcss-simple-vars`, to enable the use of Mantine's styling and custom variables.
