TITLE: RDS Parameter Group Configuration (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This JSON block configures parameters in the RDS Aurora cluster parameter group to enable logical replication. The parameters are related to replication slots, WAL senders, replication workers, and worker processes. These settings ensure that the database can handle the replication load necessary for a zero-downtime upgrade.
SOURCE: https://github.com/medplum/medplum/blob/main/packages/docs/blog/2024-11-14-zero-downtime-postgres-major-version-upgrade.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "rds.logical_replication": "1",
  "max_replication_slots": "25",
  "max_wal_senders": "25",
  "max_logical_replication_workers": "25",
  "max_worker_processes": "50"
}
```

