		Z --> ElecProc
		TestProc --> E(Free Testosterone Level)
		E2Proc --> W(Estradiol E2 Level)
		ElecProc --> F(Sodium Level)
		ElecProc --> G(Potassium Level)
		ElecProc --> H(Chloride Level)
		ElecProc --> J(Total CO2 Level)

